Forming a Professional LLC










 





The rules about who can form a professional LLC and how they are formed vary state by state. To learn the rules in your state, choose the state from the list below. You will find all the information you need about forming a professional LLC in your state, including links to forms, government agencies, and other resources.  














How to Form a Professional LLC in Connecticut
As a licensed professional in Connecticut you can structure your business as a Connecticut professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Minnesota
As a licensed professional in Minnesota you can structure your business as a Minnesota professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in New York
As a licensed professional in New York you can structure your business as a New York professional service limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in South Carolina
As a licensed professional in South Carolina you may be able to structure your business as a South Carolina professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Maryland
As a licensed professional in Maryland you can structure your business as a Maryland professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Ohio
As a licensed professional in Ohio, you can structure your business as an Ohio professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Pennsylvania
As a licensed professional in Pennsylvania you can structure your business as a Pennsylvania restricted professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Virginia
As a licensed professional in Virginia you can structure your business as a Virginia professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Michigan
As a licensed professional in Michigan you can structure your business as a Michigan professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in North Carolina
As a licensed professional in North Carolina you can structure your business as a North Carolina professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Delaware
As a licensed professional in Delaware you can structure your business as a Delaware professional limited liability company (PLLC).




How to Form a Professional LLC in Arizona
As a licensed professional in Arizona you can structure your business as an Arizona professional limited liability company (PLLC).















